name: purine-nucleoside phosphorylase
reaction: (1) purine ribonucleoside + phosphate = purine + alpha-D-ribose 1-phosphate [RN:R08368]; (2) purine 2'-deoxyribonucleoside + phosphate = purine + 2-deoxy-alpha-D-ribose 1-phosphate [RN:R10244]
comment: Specificity not completely determined. Can also catalyse ribosyltransferase reactions of the type catalysed by EC 2.4.2.5, nucleoside ribosyltransferase.
